        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Riko, do you start with the music or wait for the lyrics to be made first when you compose songs for Aqours?",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "Hmm, the lyrics come first. That's why I get a little anxious when Chika is having trouble writing them.",
            "voice_idx": "1",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "*Laugh* I can see why. You can't get to writing any music if the lyrics aren't settled.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "2"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "But she comes up with such wonderful lyrics when she mulls over them. The words are packed with her hard work and intense desire to shine.",
            "voice_idx": "2",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "I get that sense, too. My heart lights up when I listen to Aqours' songs. That includes both Chika's lyrics and your music, Riko.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "set_viewing",
            "viewing_value": "enable"
        },
        {
