        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "Now that you mention it, the Nijigasaki High School Idol Club that you're in performs solo, rather than as a group, right?",
            "voice_idx": "8",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "That's right.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "1"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "That means you're always composing songs for nine different people. Isn't that tough?",
            "voice_idx": "9",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Well, I can get away with writing fewer songs when only some of the members have scheduled live shows.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "But when everyone is performing at the same event, I have to write nine songs at once, which can be... *Laugh* Yeah, it's pretty tough.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "5"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "I'll bet it is. For Aqours, all nine of us sing the same song, so we usually only have to write one song. Even then it takes a really long time to finish composing it.",
            "voice_idx": "10",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "1"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "But writing nine songs all at once... I can't even begin to imagine what that's like.",
            "voice_idx": "11",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "I'm so exhausted at the end of it that I wonder how I'm even managing to breathe.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "2"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "I don't blame you. It does seem like it'd be quite satisfying, though.",
            "voice_idx": "12",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "1"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "It definitely is! All the Nijigasaki members tell me they love the songs I write, and it feels amazing to hear the girls finally sing them on a spectacular stage.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "And then, the audience goes wild for their performances. Seeing all of that makes me glad I wrote the songs and could have the girls perform them.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "2"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "I know how you feel. That's exactly what I thought when I performed the first song I ever composed on stage with all of Aqours.",
            "voice_idx": "13",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "When Chika's and You's voices filled the stage with the melody I created, it felt like that was enough to wash away all of my troubles.",
            "voice_idx": "14",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "unknown_select",
            "select_args": "||I think we might be on the same wavelength.|| select_1"
        },
        {
            "command": "unknown_select",
            "select_args": "||It sure does bring joy to have someone sing one of your songs.|| select_2"
