            "goto_args": "main_1"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "It sure does bring joy to have people you trust sing your songs.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "1"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "Yes, I don't think I would've been able to experience that feeling if I hadn't joined Aqours.",
            "voice_idx": "16",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "unknown_goto",
            "goto_args": "main_1"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Hey, Riko? Do you wanna come hang out at Nijigasaki High School some time? There's still so much I want to talk to you about.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Riko",
            "line": "Can I? I might just drop on by, then.",
